inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where Event_s   contains "progress"
| extend sname_input=strcat(progress_id_g,"-inputRowsPerSecond")
| extend status_input = todouble(extractjson("$.[0].inputRowsPerSecond", progress_sources_s))
| extend sname_p =strcat(progress_id_g,"-ProcRowsPerSecond")
| extend status_processed = todouble(extractjson("$.[0].processedRowsPerSecond", progress_sources_s))
| summarize avg(status_input), avg(status_processed) by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m)
| order by  TimeGenerated   asc  nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results=SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where  Event_s  contains "SparkListenerJobStart"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Job_ID_d,apptag,clusterName_s,
Submission_Time_d,TimeGenerated
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    | where Event_s contains "SparkListenerJobEnd"
    | where Job_Result_Result_s contains "JobSucceeded"
    | project Event_s,Job_ID_d,Completion_Time_d,TimeGenerated
) on Job_ID_d;
results
| extend slice=strcat(clusterName_s,"-",apptag)
| extend jobDuration=(Completion_Time_d - Submission_Time_d )/1000
| summarize avg(jobDuration) by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), slice
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results=SparkListenerEvent_CL
|  where  Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d,apptag,TimeGenerated,clusterName_s
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    |  where Event_s contains "SparkListenerStageCompleted"  
    | extend stageDuration=(Stage_Info_Completion_Time_d - Stage_Info_Submission_Time_d)/1000
) on Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d;
results
 | extend slice = strcat(clusterName_s,"-",apptag," ",Stage_Info_Stage_Name_s) 
| extend stageDuration=(Stage_Info_Completion_Time_d - Stage_Info_Submission_Time_d )/1000
| summarize avg(stageDuration) by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), slice
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let result=SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where  Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d,Stage_Info_Stage_Name_s,apptag,clusterName_s,Event_s,TimeGenerated
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    |  where Event_s contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
    | where Task_End_Reason_Reason_s contains "Success"
    | project Task_Info_Launch_Time_d,Stage_ID_d,Task_Info_Task_ID_d,Event_s,
              Task_Info_Finish_Time_d
              ) on $left.Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d == $right.Stage_ID_d;
result
| extend TaskLatency =  (Task_Info_Finish_Time_d - Task_Info_Launch_Time_d)/1000
| extend slice=strcat(clusterName_s,"-",apptag)
| summarize avg(TaskLatency)  by bin(TimeGenerated,1m),slice
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last;

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results=SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where  Event_s  contains "SparkListenerJobStart"
| extend metricsns=columnifexists("Properties_spark_metrics_namespace_s",Properties_spark_app_id_s)
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Job_ID_d,apptag,clusterName_s,TimeGenerated
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    | where Event_s contains "SparkListenerJobEnd"
    | where Job_Result_Result_s contains "JobSucceeded"
    | project Event_s,Job_ID_d,TimeGenerated
) on Job_ID_d;
results
| extend slice=strcat("#JobsCompleted ",clusterName_s,"-",apptag)
| summarize count(Job_ID_d)   by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m),slice
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results=SparkListenerEvent_CL
|  where  Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project 
Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d,apptag,TimeGenerated,clusterName_s
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    |  where Event_s contains "SparkListenerStageCompleted"  
) on Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d;
results
 | extend slice = strcat("# StagesCompleted ",clusterName_s,"-",
apptag," ",Stage_Info_Stage_Name_s)

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let result=SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d,Stage_Info_Stage_Name_s,Stage_Info_Submission_Time_d,Event_s,TimeGenerated,clusterName_s,apptag
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    |  where Event_s contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
    | where Task_End_Reason_Reason_s contains "Success"
    | project Stage_ID_d,Task_Info_Task_ID_d,
              TaskEvent=Event_s,TimeGenerated
) on $left.Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d == $right.Stage_ID_d;
result
| extend slice=strcat("#TasksCompleted ",clusterName_s,"-",apptag," ")
| summarize count(TaskEvent)  by bin(TimeGenerated,1m),slice
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| summarize dcount(Properties_spark_scheduler_pool_s) by bin(TimeGenerated,1m)

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
SparkMetric_CL
| where name_s !contains "driver" 
| where name_s contains "executorMetrics"
| extend sname=split(name_s, ".")
| extend executor=strcat(sname[1]) 
| summarize NumExecutors=dcount(executor)  by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m)
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results = SparkMetric_CL 
|  where name_s contains "executor.cpuTime" 
| extend sname=split(name_s, ".")
| extend executor=strcat("executorid:",sname[1])
| project TimeGenerated , cpuTime=count_d/1000000  ,  executor ,name_s
| join kind= inner (
    SparkMetric_CL
|  where name_s contains "executor.RunTime"
| extend sname=split(name_s, ".") 
| extend executor=strcat("executorid:",sname[1])
| project TimeGenerated , runTime=count_d  ,  executor ,name_s
) on executor, TimeGenerated;
results
| extend cpuUsage_percentage=(cpuTime/runTime)*100
| summarize ExecutorCpuTime = avg(cpuUsage_percentage) by bin(TimeGenerated, 1m), executor
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
SparkMetric_CL
| where  name_s  contains "shuffle-client.usedDirectMemory"
| extend sname=split(name_s, ".")
| extend executor=strcat("executorid:",sname[1])
| extend shuffle_client_mem_MB = value_d*1e-6
| summarize avg(shuffle_client_mem_MB)  by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), executor
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let results=SparkMetric_CL
|  where  name_s  contains "executor.memoryBytesSpilled"
| extend sname=split(name_s, ".") 
| extend executor=strcat("executorid:",sname[1])
| summarize MaxShuffleWrites=max(count_d)  by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), executor 
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last 
| join kind= inner (
    SparkMetric_CL
    |  where name_s contains "executor.memoryBytesSpilled"
    | extend sname=split(name_s, ".") 
    | extend executor=strcat("executorid:",sname[1])
| summarize MinShuffleWrites=min(count_d)  by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), executor
) on executor, TimeGenerated;
results
| extend ShuffleMemSpilled_MB=(MaxShuffleWrites-MinShuffleWrites)*1e-6
| summarize any(ShuffleMemSpilled_MB)   by bin(TimeGenerated,  1m), executor
| order by TimeGenerated asc nulls last

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
SparkLoggingEvent_CL
| where Level contains "Error"
| project TimeGenerated , Message , thread_name_s

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let result=SparkListenerEvent_CL
| where Event_s  contains "SparkListenerStageSubmitted"
| extend apptag=iif(isnotempty(Properties_spark_app_id_s),Properties_spark_app_id_s, applicationId_s)
| project Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d,Stage_Info_Stage_Name_s,Stage_Info_Submission_Time_d,Event_s,TimeGenerated,clusterName_s,apptag, Stage_Info_Number_of_Tasks_d, Stage_Info_Parent_IDs_s
| order by TimeGenerated asc  nulls last
| join kind= inner
(
    SparkListenerEvent_CL
    | where Event_s contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
    | where Task_End_Reason_Reason_s contains "Success"
    | project Task_Info_Launch_Time_d,Stage_ID_d,Task_Info_Task_ID_d,Event_s,Task_Metrics_Executor_Deserialize_Time_d,Task_Metrics_Shuffle_Read_Metrics_Fetch_Wait_Time_d,               Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_d,Task_Metrics_Shuffle_Write_Metrics_Shuffle_Write_Time_d, Task_Metrics_Result_Serialization_Time_d,Task_Info_Getting_Result_Time_d,               Task_Metrics_Shuffle_Read_Metrics_Remote_Bytes_Read_d,Task_Metrics_Shuffle_Write_Metrics_Shuffle_Bytes_Written_d,               Task_Metrics_JVM_GC_Time_d,TimeGenerated, Task_Info_Executor_ID_s
)
on $left.Stage_Info_Stage_ID_d == $right.Stage_ID_d;
let result2 = result
| extend Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s = Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_d/1000
| summarize count(Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s), percentiles(Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s,70, 90, 100) by Stage_ID_d, bin(TimeGenerated,1s)
| order by TimeGenerated, Stage_ID_d desc  nulls last;
result2
| where count_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s > 20
| extend  diff_90_70_net = percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_90 - percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_70
| extend  diff_100_90_net = percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_100 - percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_90
| extend diff_90_70_percent = (percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_90 - percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_70)/percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_70 *100
| extend diff_100_90_percent = (percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_100 -percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_90)/percentile_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s_90*100
| extend task_count = count_Task_Metrics_Executor_Run_Time_s
| project TimeGenerated, Stage_ID_d, task_count, diff_90_70_percent , diff_90_70_net,  diff_100_90_percent, diff_100_90_net
| order by TimeGenerated, Stage_ID_d asc nulls last;
